Description:
  You have been challenged by the Twin Keepers. They have split the life of their most powerful creature into two, and share one part each. Even if you kill the creature, it will revive immediately as long as its twin remains alive. They seem to have set their sights on the power of the hero of this land to make this ability more complete. You must get to the hero before they do and stop this at all costs.